        public DataProcRequirement​(java.lang.String fileType,
                           java.lang.String fileQuality,
                           java.lang.String colorType,
                           double contrast,
                           double brightness,
                           double saturation,
                           double highlights,
                           double exposure,
                           double shadows,
                           double whites,
                           double blacks,
                           double luminance,
                           double hue)
        The constructor of the data processing requirement class
        Parameters:
        fileType - the file type ("PNG", "JPEG", "RAW")
        fileQuality - the file quality ("Low", "Fine")
        colorType - the color type ("Color mode", "B&W mode")
        contrast - the constrast value (both Color and B&W modes)
        brightness - the brightness value (only Color mode)
        saturation - the saturation value (only Color mode)
        highlights - the highlight value (only B&W mode)
        exposure - the exposure value (both Color and B&W modes)
        shadows - the shadows value (only B&W mode)
        whites - the whites value (only B&W mode)
        blacks - the blacks value (only B&W mode)
        luminance - the luminance value (only Color mode)
        hue - the hue value (only Color mode)
